      • callSoapClient

        protected SoapCallReturn callSoapClient(SoapCall<Object> soapCall)
        Wraps calls to the SOAP client and listens for errors stating that the DFA token has expired. In the event that the DFA token has expired, this method will refresh the token and retry the SOAP call.
        Overrides:
